<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-2990] We should refuse query for counters at CL.ANY</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2990</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We currently do not reject writes for counters at CL.ANY, even though this is not supported (and rightly so).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12517821">CASSANDRA-2990</key>
            <summary>We should refuse query for counters at CL.ANY</summary>
